{"type":"answer","id":104338,"parentType":"question","parentId":13245,"uid":16923,"contents":"不完全是，你看中东那么多石油国，一个个富得流油，你觉得它们都是高度文明的国家吗？<br>\n<br>\n可以参考一下维基百科上发达国家的描述：发达国家的普遍特征是较高的<a href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E4%BA%BA%E7%B1%BB%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E6%8C%87%E6%95%B0/1239294\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">人类发展指数</a>、<a href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E4%BA%BA%E5%9D%87%E5%9B%BD%E6%B0%91%E7%94%9F%E4%BA%A7%E6%80%BB%E5%80%BC/4238518\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">人均国民生产总值</a>、<a href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E5%B7%A5%E4%B8%9A%E5%8C%96/2588283\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">工业化</a>水准和<a href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E5%93%81%E8%B4%A8/4195670\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">生活品质</a>。借由开发<a href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E8%87%AA%E7%84%B6%E8%B5%84%E6%BA%90\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">自然资源</a>也可以达到较高的人均<a href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E5%9B%BD%E6%B0%91%E7%94%9F%E4%BA%A7%E6%80%BB%E5%80%BC/287236\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">国民生产总值</a>和人类发展指数，但未必属于发达国家（比如<a href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E6%96%87%E8%8E%B1/212618\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">文莱</a>、<a href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E6%B2%99%E7%89%B9%E9%98%BF%E6%8B%89%E4%BC%AF/201335\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">沙特阿拉伯</a>、<a href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E5%8D%A1%E5%A1%94%E5%B0%94/204275\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">卡塔尔</a>等国）。","date":"2019-12-14","agreeCount":5,"discussionCount":0}